            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x2DB63D9F<!--The idea of Unfinished Business didn't really appeal or matter much to Kai before he died, you know. It's weird because he's so practical but also sure of what he wants that you'd think he'd have wanted to nail it down. Personally, that's not workable for me. I've wanted to make sure I get to do all the things I want to do in life while I have the chance.--></T>
                  <T>0x95C1CACB<!--After Kai died, Takama started wearing a crow outfit a lot. I remember Layne stopping by and asking what that was about and a lot of questions about how the family was handling grief. Grief definitely has a lot of permutations, doesn't it? But I think Takama wanted to feel connected to his father and that's that. --></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
