            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xDFFB45BF<!--I'm not sure if it's jitters since Kai passed away or if it's something else, but I have this feeling like Grim's on my tail, too. The other day I was hit by lightning and then, I was electrocuted when I turned on the TV! I was thinking about going stargazing in Whispering Glen, but I don't think that's a great plan.--></T>
                  <T>0xCBB60543<!--We moved to Whispering Glen when we wanted to have life at a slightly slower pace, and I absolutely love it here. The Final Draught is where I love to go to unwind after a long dayâ€”and I've even seen Sims hold wakes there. It's hard to miss the Ancestor cliff, though I make it a point to go out and observe it for a while anyway. I mean, you gotta go to the Moon Revelry festival sometimes, right?--></T>
                  <T>0xCD2F23DA<!--Last time I took Takama to the Ravenwood Family Day, we went for a long walk afterward and ended up stumbling across Edith near her well. Takama was transfixed by her, but I really just wanted to get him out of there; I was pretty scared myself. That head tilt... --></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
